    "MissionType": {
        "UUID": "5e727c38-d43e-445f-95b2-a971428dd06d",
        "Name": "Resource Drive - ArcCorp"
    },
    "MissionGiver": "ArcCorp",
    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: GET OUR LARGE CARGO BACK",
    "Description": "Hey, El here.\n\nGot a big problem. Outlaws have taken out one of our transport ships and stolen the cargo.\n\nThe resources on that ship were flagged for that UEE initiative and we\u2019re going to be in a lot of trouble unless we get them back.\n\nFortunately, I had the good sense to put tags on the cargo, so we\u2019ve managed to track it down to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. Corporate has approved a sliding pay scale based on whatever you can bring back. Ideally that\u2019s all <EM4>~mission(ItemsToRecover) cargo boxes (all ~mission(MaxBoxSize) SCU or smaller)</EM4>, but we\u2019ll take what we can get. Once you\u2019ve got the cargo loaded up onto a decently size hauler, drop it off at a freight elevator at: <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address|ListAll)</EM4>. One of my colleagues will take care of the rest.\n\nThese outlaws mean business, so make sure you\u2019re stocked up on weapons, supplies, and a <EM4>few friends</EM4> before you head out.\n\nGood luck! I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll do great.\n\n\nElla Tieno\nContractor Liaison Officer\nArcCorp",
